		}</style><style type="text/css" id="custom-background-css">body.custom-background { background-color: #ffffff; }</style><link rel="icon" href="https://blog.prif.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cropped-hsfk_ball_blog_2-32x32.png" sizes="32x32" /><link rel="icon" href="https://blog.prif.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cropped-hsfk_ball_blog_2-300x300.png" sizes="192x192" /><link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="https://blog.prif.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cropped-hsfk_ball_blog_2-300x300.png" /><meta name="msapplication-TileImage" content="https://blog.prif.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cropped-hsfk_ball_blog_2-300x300.png" /></head><body class="post-template-default single single-post postid-845 single-format-standard custom-background group-blog"> <a class="sr-only sr-only-focusable" href="#content">Skip to main content</a><div id="page" class="hfeed site"><header id="masthead" class="site-header" role="banner"><nav class="navbar navbar-default
 " role="navigation"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="site-navigation-inner col-sm-12"><div class="navbar-header"><div id="logo"> <a href="https://blog.prif.org/"><img src="https://blog.prif.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/cropped-PRIF-Blog_Schriftzug_v4.png"  height="190" width="750" alt="PRIF BLOG"/></a></div> <button type="button" class="btn navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-ex1-collapse"> <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span> <span class="icon-bar"></span> <span class="icon-bar"></span> <span class="icon-bar"></span> </button></div><div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-ex1-collapse"><ul id="menu-kopf" class="nav navbar-nav"><li id="menu-item-362" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-home menu-item-has-children menu-item-362 dropdown"><a title="Startseite" href="https://blog.prif.org/">Blog</a><span class="caret sparkling-dropdown"></span><ul role="menu" class=" dropdown-menu"><li id="menu-item-390" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-390"><a href="https://blog.prif.org/ueber-dieses-blog/">Über uns</a></li><li id="menu-item-388" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-privacy-policy menu-item-388"><a href="https://blog.prif.org/datenschutz/">Datenschutzerklärung</a></li><li id="menu-item-389" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-389"><a href="https://blog.prif.org/impressum/">Impressum</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-item-1728" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-1728 dropdown"><a href="https://blog.prif.org/reihen/">Reihen</a><span class="caret sparkling-dropdown"></span><ul role="menu" class=" dropdown-menu"><li id="menu-item-3774" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3774"><a href="https://blog.prif.org/reihen/corona-krisen/">Corona-Krise(n)</a></li><li id="menu-ite